tspan.tspan: Auto racing has a
rich history; a history
of challenge seekers
and boundary pushers,
of undaunted precision drivers
and fearless mavericks.
As part of the lineage of racing,
its our duty as drivers to test the
boundaries of speed and the
limits of our machines.
Until now, we have been restricted by our
narrow rulesets and limited technology,
piloting machines using the same basic principles
as those of years past-- but the future is calling,
and it isnt bound by historys limitations.
The next evolution in racing vehicle technology
will be unlike anything youve driven before.
These vehicles are agile, smart, and fine-tuned
to race in the harshest of conditions
and the wildest of environments. They have capabilities
far beyond those of prior generations, and performance
youll need to see to believe.
Its a future that will require every ounce
of a drivers nerves and focus to conquer.
Its a future thats closer than you think.
